title: ACC Pick'n Kitten: Biased for Tigers
text:
You must enter the characters with black color that stand out from the other characters By Joe Ovies 
Predicting the outcome of football games is difficult due to the simple fact that sports are unpredictable. 
However, the capricious nature of our national pastimes doesn't stop us from tempting fortune. Whether it's for entertainment purposes only or an attempt to be the smartest person in the room, everybody loves offering up their stone-cold locks of the century of the week. 
Rather than relying on any sort of insight into these matchups, I will use my cat as a prognosticator. After taking last week off to deal with a hairball, his overall record stands at 6-6 for the season. NC State vs. Louisville North Carolina vs. Georgia Tech Duke vs. Boston College
